        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Addressing Social Isolation and Loneliness in Older Adults Act of 2023 or the Addressing SILO Act of 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill provides funding through FY2028 for grants to prevent and address social isolation or loneliness among older adults and individuals with disabilities through education, outreach, and community-based interventions. The Department of Health and Human Services must award these grants to area agencies on aging and community-based organizations.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
